  .ts-sub-header-02.border-bottom
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-12
          .sub-header-inner
            h2 About Us
            nav(aria-label="breadcrumb")
              ol.ts-breadcrumb-01
                li.breadcrumb-item
                  a(href="home_01.html") Home
                li.breadcrumb-item.active(aria-current="page") About Us

  .home-01-about-us.bg--white.py-5.py-lg-7
    .container
      .row
        .col-xl-7.col-lg-6.d-flex.align-items-center.mb-5.mb-lg-0
          img.thumb(src='images/mockup-blanka-02.png', alt='cover')
        .col-xl-5.col-lg-6.pl-lg-5
          .ts-section-heading-01.mb-4
            h2 What Can Blanka Offer?
          p.mb-lg-4.pb-2 The highest levels of service and technical expertise from experts all over the world. Together we understand the challenges you face and the importance of firm decisions... We will help you to find the right solutions, quickly and effectively.
          ul.list-style-01.list-square.color.mb-lg-4.mb-3
            li FULLY RESPONSIVE
            li CLEAN DESIGN
            li PORTFOLIO COLUMNS
            li DEEP RESEARCH
            li 07 HOME PAGES
            li AND MANY MORE...
          a(href="about_01.html").ts-btn.btn-color1 Contact Us
            i.ts-icon.la.la-plus.pl-3

  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-12
        .border-bottom

  .about-01-additional.py-lg-7.py-5
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-6.pr-lg-5.mb-5.mb-lg-0
          .ts-section-heading-01
            h2 Additional Information
          p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Pellentesque quam ipsum, elementum nec ipsum et, consequat blandit neque. Duis sed condimentum elit. Cras fermentum dolor est. Pellentesque accumsan placerat orci ac tempor. Vestibulum in justo blandit lacus suscipit consequat. Cras placerat ligula porta iaculis iaculis. Donec ut lorem at magna mollis vestibulum nec id orci. Nulla in dolor gravida justo viverra lacinia. Donec convallis nisi in velit ullamcorper interdum. Mauris blandit pulvinar odio non euismod. Cras viverra sodales pretium.
