          br
          a(href="#").ts-btn.btn-color1 
            | Discover more
            i.ts-icon.la.la-angle-right
        .col-lg-6.pl-lg-5
          .ts-section-heading-01
            h2 Our Commitment
          p.mb-5 We lead with a commitment to quality and consistency across our global network, bringing a passion for client success and a purpose to serve and improve the communities in which member firms operate.
          .process-wrap
            .ts-progress-wrapper.mb-4.js-progress-bar
              .ts-progress-title-wrap
                h5.ts-progress-title PARTNERSHIP
                .ts-progress-info  
                  span.ts-progress-percentage
                  i.ts-progress-unit %
              .ts-progress
                .progress-bar.bg--color1(role='progressbar' aria-valuenow='95', aria-valuemin='0', aria-valuemax='100')
